{"info": {"author": "Jayden Smith", "author_email": "jayden@intelliscale.com.au", "bugtrack_url": null, "classifiers": ["Environment :: Web Environment", "Framework :: Django", "Framework :: Django :: 1.8", "Framework :: Django :: 1.9", "Intended Audience :: Developers", "License :: OSI Approved :: MIT License", "Operating System :: OS Independent", "Programming Language :: Python", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3.4", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3.5", "Topic :: Internet :: WWW/HTTP", "Topic :: Internet :: WWW/HTTP :: Dynamic Content"], "description": "===============\nWagtail Froala\n===============\n\nExtends Wagtail to use the amazing Froala editor.\nThis Wagtail extension requires Wagtail 1.5.x, as it uses ``WAGTAILADMIN_RICH_TEXT_EDITORS``.\n\nInstallation\n============\n\nRun the command ``pip install wagtailfroala``\n\nAdd ``wagtailfroala`` to your ``INSTALLED_APPS``.\n\nAdd ``wagtailfroala.rich_text.FroalaRichTextArea`` to ``WAGTAILADMIN_RICH_TEXT_EDITORS`` in your settings.\n\nFor example, to use Froala for all ``RichTextField`` and ``RichTextBlock`` instances:\n\n.. code-block:: python\n\n    WAGTAILADMIN_RICH_TEXT_EDITORS = {\n        'default': {\n            'WIDGET': 'wagtailfroala.rich_text.FroalaRichTextArea',\n            'OPTIONS': {\n                'key': 'xxxxxxxxxxxx'\n             }\n        }\n    }\n\nOr, to use Froala only for defined instances...\n\n.. code-block:: python\n    \n    WAGTAILADMIN_RICH_TEXT_EDITORS = {\n        'default': {\n            'WIDGET': 'wagtail.wagtailadmin.rich_text.HalloRichTextArea'\n        },\n        'froala': {\n            'WIDGET': 'wagtailfroala.rich_text.FroalaRichTextArea',\n            'OPTIONS': {\n                'key': 'xxxxxxxxxxxx',\n                'toolbarButtons': [\n                    'paragraphFormat', 'fontFamily', 'bold', 'italic',\n                    'underline', 'formatOL', 'formatUL', 'align',\n                    'color', '|', 'insertHR', 'insertLink', '|', 'undo', 'redo'\n                ]\n            }\n        },\n        'froala_small': {\n            'WIDGET': 'wagtailfroala.rich_text.FroalaRichTextArea',\n            'OPTIONS': {\n                'key': 'xxxxxxxxxxxx',\n                'toolbarButtons': ['fontFamily', 'bold', 'italic', 'underline', 'color', '|', 'insertLink'],\n                'editorClass': 'editor-small'\n            }\n        }\n    }\n\n.. code-block:: python\n\n    html_field = RichTextField(editor='froala')\n    stream_field = StreamField([\n        ('html', RichTextBlock(editor='froala_small'))\n    ])\n\nOptions\n-------\n\nYou will need to ensure that the ``key`` option is correctly set with your Froala license key.\n\nBy default, Codemirror HTML syntax highlighting is enabled, you can disable it if you wish.\n\n.. code-block:: python\n    \n    FROALA_CODEMIRROR = False\n\nFont Awesome is required by Froala for toolbar icons, so it is included by default. If you don't want to include it or already have a version included, you can disable it.\n\n.. code-block:: python\n    \n    FROALA_FONT_AWESOME = False\n\nTo Do\n-------\n- [ ] Implement image replace button.\n- [ ] Incoorperate Froala events https://www.froala.com/wysiwyg-editor/docs/events.\n\n\nPlease feel free to contribute.", "description_content_type": "", "docs_url": null, "download_url": "", "downloads": {"last_day": -1, "last_month": -1, "last_week": -1}, "home_page": "https://github.com/jaydensmith/wagtailfroala", "keywords": "", "license": "MIT License", "maintainer": "", "maintainer_email": "", "name": "wagtailfroala", "package_url": "https://pypi.org/project/wagtailfroala/", "platform": "", "project_url": "https://pypi.org/project/wagtailfroala/", "project_urls": {"Homepage": "https://github.com/jaydensmith/wagtailfroala"}, "release_url": "https://pypi.org/project/wagtailfroala/0.2.11/", "requires_dist": null, "requires_python": "", "summary": "Extends Wagtail to use the Froala WYSIWYG editor in RichTextFields/RichTextBlocks.", "version": "0.2.11", "yanked": false, "html_description": "<div class=\"project-description\">\n            <p>Extends Wagtail to use the amazing Froala editor.\nThis Wagtail extension requires Wagtail 1.5.x, as it uses <tt>WAGTAILADMIN_RICH_TEXT_EDITORS</tt>.</p>\n<div id=\"installation\">\n<h2>Installation</h2>\n<p>Run the command <tt>pip install wagtailfroala</tt></p>\n<p>Add <tt>wagtailfroala</tt> to your <tt>INSTALLED_APPS</tt>.</p>\n<p>Add <tt>wagtailfroala.rich_text.FroalaRichTextArea</tt> to <tt>WAGTAILADMIN_RICH_TEXT_EDITORS</tt> in your settings.</p>\n<p>For example, to use Froala for all <tt>RichTextField</tt> and <tt>RichTextBlock</tt> instances:</p>\n<pre><span class=\"n\">WAGTAILADMIN_RICH_TEXT_EDITORS</span> <span class=\"o\">=</span> <span class=\"p\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"s1\">'default'</span><span class=\"p\">:</span> <span class=\"p\">{</span>\n        <span class=\"s1\">'WIDGET'</span><span class=\"p\">:</span> <span class=\"s1\">'wagtailfroala.rich_text.FroalaRichTextArea'</span><span class=\"p\">,</span>\n        <span class=\"s1\">'OPTIONS'</span><span class=\"p\">:</span> <span class=\"p\">{</span>\n            <span class=\"s1\">'key'</span><span class=\"p\">:</span> <span class=\"s1\">'xxxxxxxxxxxx'</span>\n         <span class=\"p\">}</span>\n    <span class=\"p\">}</span>\n<span class=\"p\">}</span>\n</pre>\n<p>Or, to use Froala only for defined instances\u2026</p>\n<pre><span class=\"n\">WAGTAILADMIN_RICH_TEXT_EDITORS</span> <span class=\"o\">=</span> <span class=\"p\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"s1\">'default'</span><span class=\"p\">:</span> <span class=\"p\">{</span>\n        <span class=\"s1\">'WIDGET'</span><span class=\"p\">:</span> <span class=\"s1\">'wagtail.wagtailadmin.rich_text.HalloRichTextArea'</span>\n    <span class=\"p\">},</span>\n    <span class=\"s1\">'froala'</span><span class=\"p\">:</span> <span class=\"p\">{</span>\n        <span class=\"s1\">'WIDGET'</span><span class=\"p\">:</span> <span class=\"s1\">'wagtailfroala.rich_text.FroalaRichTextArea'</span><span class=\"p\">,</span>\n        <span class=\"s1\">'OPTIONS'</span><span class=\"p\">:</span> <span class=\"p\">{</span>\n            <span class=\"s1\">'key'</span><span class=\"p\">:</span> <span class=\"s1\">'xxxxxxxxxxxx'</span><span class=\"p\">,</span>\n            <span class=\"s1\">'toolbarButtons'</span><span class=\"p\">:</span> <span class=\"p\">[</span>\n                <span class=\"s1\">'paragraphFormat'</span><span class=\"p\">,</span> <span class=\"s1\">'fontFamily'</span><span class=\"p\">,</span> <span class=\"s1\">'bold'</span><span class=\"p\">,</span> <span class=\"s1\">'italic'</span><span class=\"p\">,</span>\n                <span class=\"s1\">'underline'</span><span class=\"p\">,</span> <span class=\"s1\">'formatOL'</span><span class=\"p\">,</span> <span class=\"s1\">'formatUL'</span><span class=\"p\">,</span> <span class=\"s1\">'align'</span><span class=\"p\">,</span>\n                <span class=\"s1\">'color'</span><span class=\"p\">,</span> <span class=\"s1\">'|'</span><span class=\"p\">,</span> <span class=\"s1\">'insertHR'</span><span class=\"p\">,</span> <span class=\"s1\">'insertLink'</span><span class=\"p\">,</span> <span class=\"s1\">'|'</span><span class=\"p\">,</span> <span class=\"s1\">'undo'</span><span class=\"p\">,</span> <span class=\"s1\">'redo'</span>\n            <span class=\"p\">]</span>\n        <span class=\"p\">}</span>\n    <span class=\"p\">},</span>\n    <span class=\"s1\">'froala_small'</span><span class=\"p\">:</span> <span class=\"p\">{</span>\n        <span class=\"s1\">'WIDGET'</span><span class=\"p\">:</span> <span class=\"s1\">'wagtailfroala.rich_text.FroalaRichTextArea'</span><span class=\"p\">,</span>\n        <span class=\"s1\">'OPTIONS'</span><span class=\"p\">:</span> <span class=\"p\">{</span>\n            <span class=\"s1\">'key'</span><span class=\"p\">:</span> <span class=\"s1\">'xxxxxxxxxxxx'</span><span class=\"p\">,</span>\n            <span class=\"s1\">'toolbarButtons'</span><span class=\"p\">:</span> <span class=\"p\">[</span><span class=\"s1\">'fontFamily'</span><span class=\"p\">,</span> <span class=\"s1\">'bold'</span><span class=\"p\">,</span> <span class=\"s1\">'italic'</span><span class=\"p\">,</span> <span class=\"s1\">'underline'</span><span class=\"p\">,</span> <span class=\"s1\">'color'</span><span class=\"p\">,</span> <span class=\"s1\">'|'</span><span class=\"p\">,</span> <span class=\"s1\">'insertLink'</span><span class=\"p\">],</span>\n            <span class=\"s1\">'editorClass'</span><span class=\"p\">:</span> <span class=\"s1\">'editor-small'</span>\n        <span class=\"p\">}</span>\n    <span class=\"p\">}</span>\n<span class=\"p\">}</span>\n</pre>\n<pre><span class=\"n\">html_field</span> <span class=\"o\">=</span> <span class=\"n\">RichTextField</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">editor</span><span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"s1\">'froala'</span><span class=\"p\">)</span>\n<span class=\"n\">stream_field</span> <span class=\"o\">=</span> <span class=\"n\">StreamField</span><span class=\"p\">([</span>\n    <span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"s1\">'html'</span><span class=\"p\">,</span> <span class=\"n\">RichTextBlock</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">editor</span><span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"s1\">'froala_small'</span><span class=\"p\">))</span>\n<span class=\"p\">])</span>\n</pre>\n<div id=\"options\">\n<h3>Options</h3>\n<p>You will need to ensure that the <tt>key</tt> option is correctly set with your Froala license key.</p>\n<p>By default, Codemirror HTML syntax highlighting is enabled, you can disable it if you wish.</p>\n<pre><span class=\"n\">FROALA_CODEMIRROR</span> <span class=\"o\">=</span> <span class=\"kc\">False</span>\n</pre>\n<p>Font Awesome is required by Froala for toolbar icons, so it is included by default. If you don\u2019t want to include it or already have a version included, you can disable it.</p>\n<pre><span class=\"n\">FROALA_FONT_AWESOME</span> <span class=\"o\">=</span> <span class=\"kc\">False</span>\n</pre>\n</div>\n<div id=\"to-do\">\n<h3>To Do</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>[ ] Implement image replace button.</li>\n<li>[ ] Incoorperate Froala events <a href=\"https://www.froala.com/wysiwyg-editor/docs/events\" rel=\"nofollow\">https://www.froala.com/wysiwyg-editor/docs/events</a>.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Please feel free to contribute.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n          </div>"}, "last_serial": 3904463, "releases": {"0.1": [{"comment_text": "", "digests": {"md5": "9050819c437198b3b8c5a67aa8e30d71", "sha256": "ae8e4401d0be19eb77200f46fa6b24b674777946b06ecd646b6dfda3a1bcb6ba"}, "downloads": -1, "filename": "wagtailfroala-0.1.tar.gz", "has_sig": false, "md5_digest": "9050819c437198b3b8c5a67aa8e30d71", "packagetype": "sdist", "python_version": "source", "requires_python": null, "size": 1966, "upload_time": "2016-06-03T01:01:04", "upload_time_iso_8601": "2016-06-03T01:01:04.981534Z", "url": "https://files.pythonhosted.org/packages/06/c3/a428a30ebbdc1dce778494d29f700c5ddfab1c0a4840cc288c65d62e008b/wagtailfroala-0.1.tar.gz", "yanked": false}], "0.2": [{"comment_text": "", "digests": {"md5": "6a6a283d7c06c838aa9b60ec4259269d", "sha256": "57692eb5e0d2d39916772d691c4e7e7001b3d3f941fdf359d2f2f26e12b4a5c3"}, "downloads": -1, "filename": "wagtailfroala-0.2.tar.gz", "has_sig": false, "md5_digest": "6a6a283d7c06c838aa9b60ec4259269d", "packagetype": "sdist", "python_version": "source", "requires_python": null, "size": 325692, "upload_time": "2016-06-03T01:08:31", "upload_time_iso_8601": "2016-06-03T01:08:31.819924Z", "url": "https://files.pythonhosted.org/packages/27/3f/dc0d1745ecf5fa1371787a82da679be8703beae87226f934eeee107ad441/wagtailfroala-0.2.tar.gz", "yanked": false}], "0.2.1": [{"comment_text": "", "digests": {"md5": "8945c0d4e0ded5b7f095ecc8f334fdc8", "sha256": "ec35786e0e3b2904af3b57c6be63915711a4d3e61de4d87fb28427750e742cfe"}, "downloads": -1, "filename": "wagtail